{"tid":2106731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛打手出沒注意，今次係吹𠝹票吹本土","createTime":"2020-07-13T13:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T13:47:51.000Z","uid":2879,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"140a93b01740a13515ab5abd3385f8bb360e9e1f","tid":2106731,"uid":2879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"投票結果唔會盡如人意<br />\n但呢個係就係民意<br />\n原本就係泛民初選，點解仲要分本土非本土？<br />\n唔洗人分化，自己就分化左標籤埋，對家只係會偷笑。<br />\n另外，有班人又話某啲人𠝹票，又話某啲人唔值，繼而放負。<br />\n一個公佈就突然間牛鬼蛇神出晒黎又屌呢樣果樣，我諗呢一排都會不斷圍繞呢單野係咁吹風，屌黎屌去，最後自亂陣腳，大家各位睇路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada9fc2adeba2a2140a085365a8b2872dfb95aec","tid":2106731,"uid":2879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90e798672e79bd0f65d7a679485491d2466f21b5","tid":2106731,"uid":2879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d35b73d93de0813270b0b4e5c6c55c147ddfa48","tid":2106731,"uid":2879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10d91c9b9aba451139835bdbabca42a512dd612b","tid":2106731,"uid":2879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6de3b63f81c6a8b1db5eddbd21d861d093e1f27f","tid":2106731,"uid":130190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a018f65c4208b6d188c5bc87ed1509ce239d512c","tid":2106731,"uid":32645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"最撚唔尊重初選結果嘅就係某啲連登仔"},{"pid":"ca6cc1b0751b6818c7d83a13b7294f5872779480","tid":2106731,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"421098bddeddd12cf1b5a07f0adffd0c2cbaea97","